827
00:33:40,687 --> 00:33:42,773
- - That's right.
- even though it's the same stone.

828
00:33:42,856 --> 00:33:45,275
Every stone in the world
became my stepping stone.

829
00:33:45,359 --> 00:33:46,735
- - Your view changed.
- Yes.

830
00:33:46,818 --> 00:33:50,364
My attitude toward the world
completely changed.

831
00:33:50,447 --> 00:33:53,200
- - My life became something different.
- I see.

